name: ShibaX
description: Memecoin project on MultiversX blockchain. Description of ShibaX project: ShibaX is a memecoin project associated with a collection of NFTs. XSHIB is listed on all MultiversX exchanges. Hodlers can now stake their tokens and NFTs. The goal of the ShibaX project is to unite the community around the $XSHIB token through a DApp aiming to be the reference on MultiversX. The DApp is currently under construction, with more details to come.
